  "changelogHtml": "<h3 id=\"1.8.0\" data-text=\"Version 1.8.0\" tabindex=\"-1\">Version 1.8.0</h3>\n<p>May 14, 2024</p>\n<p><code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">androidx.annotation:annotation-*:1.8.0</code> is released. Version 1.8.0 contains <a href=\"https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/support/+log/2f0179ef63aef86044266c1445541db90a410052..4e5e9e3ddec39fb6f9f34c89b1b4f9b58a1ab627/annotation/annotation\">these commits</a>.</p>\n<p><strong>Important changes since 1.7.0</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Added <a href=\"https://developer.android.com/reference/kotlin/androidx/annotation/ReplaceWith\"><code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">@ReplaceWith</code></a> annotation to express replacements for deprecated APIs</li>\n<li>The <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">@MainThread</code> annotation has been moved to the common source set.</li>\n</ul>",
